sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client as IDE Client
    participant LS as Language Server
    participant Renderer as ConfigHtmlRenderer

    Note over User, Client: Configuration Flow
    User->>Client: Trigger "Snyk: Configure"
    Client->>LS: ExecuteCommand(snyk.workspace.configuration)
    LS->>LS: config.CurrentConfig()
    LS->>Renderer: GetConfigHtml(Settings)
    Renderer-->>LS: HTML String
    LS->>Client: window/showDocument(snyk://settings)
    Client->>User: Display HTML Configuration Dialog

    Note over User, Client: Save Flow
    User->>Client: Edit Settings & Click Save
    Client->>Client: JS: ${ideSaveConfig}(JSON)
    Client->>Client: Save Settings to File/Store
    Client->>LS: workspace/didChangeConfiguration
    LS->>LS: Update Internal Configuration

